data.description: Nestled in the heart of North Ogden, this residence offers an extraordinary living experience that combines comfort and captivating views. The expansive living room, flooded with natural light, opens up to breathtaking views through large windows. Three generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and privacy. The unfinished basement offers the potential for customization. Step outside onto the great deck and overlook the ample backyard space, perfect for morning coffee or entertaining guests. Nature lovers will appreciate the immediate trail access located just south; this home seamlessly combines suburban serenity with urban convenience.
